Title: Mother Thinks the Birds Are After Her
Plot: Nancy has relocated to the border in search of a new life but she soon finds her past to be inescapable. Both problems and people follow her on her journey, but some have finally been left behind.
ParentalRatingReason: R18 Drug use and offensive language
GuestStars: Albert Brooks, Joey Wagner Luthman, Andrew Rothenberg, Heather Marie Zagone
